%h1='Welcome'

%p
  This is the home of Ruby Users of Minnesota &mdash; a fine group of 
  Ruby enthusiasts from around the
  Twin Cities metro area, or pretty much wherever they feel like 
  driving from. 


%p
  You'll want to 
  =link_to "login", new_session_path
  or
  =link_to "sign up", new_user_path
  to use any of the nifty features, like the
  =link_to "help wanted", :controller=>'opening'
  , 
  =link_to "events", :controller=>'event'
  or 
  =link_to "member list", :controller=>'user', :action=>'list'
  and
  =link_to "for-hire", :controller=>"for_hire"
  sections. 

%p
  To join the mailing list, just send mail to
  %a{:href=>"mailto:ruby.mn+subscribe@ruby.mn"}='ruby.mn+subscribe@ruby.mn'

%p
  Our group meets on the 
  %b
    last Monday of each month at 7 PM 
  (come early to hack Ruby code).  
  %b
    Our meetings are held at:
  %div#meeting-place
    %span.big
      %b
      %a{:href=>'http://www.refactr.com', :target=>'_blank'}
        Refactr
    %br/
    %a{:id=>'maplink', :href=>'#map'}
      Eleven North-East Fourth Street
    %br/
    Suite 300
    %br/
    Minneapolis, MN 55413
    %br/
    Phone: 612-605-9740


-if defined?(@events) and !@events.empty?
  %h2='Announcements'
  -if !current_user.nil?
    %p=link_to "Add a New Event", new_user_event_path(current_user)
  =render :partial=>"events/event", :collection=>@events
